AdminCommands.does: will executed given command, check Admin.js for commandlist

leaguegetgame.does: gives you your (or leagueName's) current league game

neko.does: gives you a random Post from r/neko!

osuplays.does: gives you your(or osuName's) 5 best osu plays

osurecent.does: gives you your (or osuName's) most recent Play (passed or not passed)

padoru.does: answers your Callings for the almighty Being

play.does: plays a YT-Video in your Channel

poll2.does: gives you a poll based on your title (optional: with custom options)

rngsub.does: gives you a random Post (of the subreddit)

stop.does: Stops the Music in your Channel
